                     Senator John Ensign, a Republican from of Nevada, right and Senator John McCain, a Republican from Arizona, listen during a hearing on Wall Street and the financial crisis in Washington, D.C., on April 27, 2010. Photographer: Andrew Harrer/Bloomberg  
                           

     
